reviewText: This is an old concert from the 1960s, very nostalgic for me. Terrible production values, too much volume, black and white in low resolution--looks like it may have been taken off a TV show. Nonetheless, very rewarding for those of us who remember Joan back in the early days.

Joan Baez has always been one of my favorite singers.  As expected, this DVD met all my expectation.  It arrived just within a few days after I placed my order in good shape.  The seller took care of my order immediately,  I look forward dealing with the seller again.  Thanks.
